        <Parent_String>Fulbe (culture or style) [300015890], Western Sudanese fringe-dwelling peoples [300015888], Western Sudanese [300015846], West African (general) [300015845], African by cultural or regional designation [300121001], African (general, continental cultures) [300015647], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
